snippet.title: DO NOT PASS GO - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's finally here! The FINAL of the three Parody Horror Games that I promised to create over a year ago! It's available right now on Itchio and GameJOLT! Go get it!

Play DO NOT PASS GO on Itch.io!
https://microhorrorarcade.itch.io/do-not-pass-go

Play DO NOT PASS GO on GameJOLT!
https://gamejolt.com/games/Do-Not-Pass-Go/577858

Go support me on Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/MicroHorrorArcade

Go follow me on GameJOLT!
https://gamejolt.com/@MicroHorrorArcade

Go follow me on Itch.io!
https://microhorrorarcade.itch.io/

Go follow me on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/JayskiBean
